"values by Erik Baker, _Immersed_ Vol. 3, No. 3.]"
msgstr ""
"link:http://www.tek-dive.com/portal/upload/M-Values.pdf[Understanding M-"
"values by Erik Baker, _Immersed_ Vol. 3, No. 3.]"

