"articles/5037-gradient-factors-for-dummies.html[Gradient factors for "
"dummies, by Kevin Watts]"
msgstr ""
"link:http://www.rebreatherworld.com/general-and-new-to-rebreather-"
"articles/5037-gradient-factors-for-dummies.html[Gradient factors for "
"dummies, by Kevin Watts]"

